                Mr. Churchill (Woodford)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-fe829c06-a472-4b68-98b5-f8aa06ac70ec" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
