                Sir A. Duncan
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-227f8dfb-1c34-46d6-bc28-900aac5ef18f" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1946-05-28/debates/ed7c02b5-4e15-43c6-b024-6071b6c10e17/IronAndSteelIndustry#contribution-227f8dfb-1c34-46d6-bc28-900aac5ef18f">
