                Lieut-Colonel Sir Walter Smiles  (Down)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-ed2b4b0a-b3d8-448d-8271-d527e9a6c60b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
