<p class="">The whole essence of the Bretton Woods international trade agreement is fixing of prices, as has been seen with commodities.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-aa6d19af-dce2-4ccd-b010-6e773a496c3b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
