<p class="">I think the hon. Member is misrepresenting the speech of my hon. Friend the Member for Monmouth (Mr. P. Thorneycroft) in saying that he praised monopolies. I think that when the hon. Member reads HANSARD tomorrow, he will wish to withdraw his remark. It may be that he misunderstood the arguments used by my hon. Friend, who certainly did not praise monopolies.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
