            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-45de7529-f776-44c3-b4ac-cd5f3fad916e">
                Mr. Kirkwood  (Dumbarton Burghs)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-45de7529-f776-44c3-b4ac-cd5f3fad916e" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
