        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-52b1cf11-0d9e-41c9-819d-e15b602287e8'>
            
<p class="">The House divided: Ayes, 338; Noes, 184.</p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
